decks.notes: The main idea of this deck is to control the game by countering the opponent's spells, disrupting their plans, and using Ertai Resurrected's ability to sacrifice creatures in order to counter spells. The deck includes a variety of counterspells, removal spells, and disruptive cards to keep the opponent on the back foot. It also includes card advantage engines like Snapcaster Mage and Ancestral Vision to ensure the player has the resources needed to maintain control. Additionally, there are creatures like True-Name Nemesis and Vendilion Clique to apply pressure on the opponent while still offering control elements.Overall, the deck aims to out-value and out-control the opponent to secure victory in a one-on-one match.
